publicwhip.spmotion: *S2M-1316 Linda Fabiani: East Kilbride Superwomen-That the Parliament congratulates East Kilbride Ladies Hockey Team on winning six out of seven tournaments this season, Glasgow High/Kelvinside Annual Sevens Tournament, West District Indoor League, West District Indoor Cup, West District League Division 1 Championship, Scottish Hockey Union District League Championship and the West District League Cup; further congratulates retiring team captain Elaine Goldie on such an achievement in the final year of her stewardship, and sends best wishes to the team for all future success.
S2M-1316 East Kilbride Superwomen (lodged on 14 May 2004) Mr Adam Ingram*
S2M-1316 East Kilbride Superwomen (lodged on 14 May 2004) Carolyn Leckie*, Michael Matheson*
S2M-1316 East Kilbride Superwomen (lodged on 14 May 2004) Donald Gorrie*, Alex Neil*, John Swinburne*
